  https://logiclab.jira.com/browse/BJONASBN-53

- Added Test::CPAN::Changes test (t/changes.t), implementing automatic integrity test of 
  the Changes file, see also BJONASBN-50 [BJONASBN-52]

  https://logiclab.jira.com/browse/BJONASBN-52

- Added Test::Kwalitee test (t/kwalitee.t) [BJONASBN-55]

  https://logiclab.jira.com/browse/BJONASBN-55
  

