1.01 2010-09-04

- Bugfix release, update not required

- [BJONASBN-25] addressed failing test. Adhering to documentation from
  Module::Build on requirements needed for configuration


1.00 2010-09-01

- Initial release, new packaging

- [BJONASBN-21] readdressed, POD now nicely formatted again

- Renamed distribution to Task::BeLike::JONASBN [BJONASBN-22]
  Bundle::JONASBN, will eventually be removed from CPAN, but I will leave it
  there for some time. I will not support it any longer. Task::BeLike::JONASBN
  will be the new distribution

- Implemented respect for build action, so the contents section in the 
  Perl module is auto-generated based on the custom build module
  Module::Build::Bundle [BJONASBN-16]

